---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Sidebar from '../../components/Sidebar.astro';
const title = "Chemo-dynamical reconstruction methods";
import WikiLink from '../../components/WikiLink.astro';
---
<Base title={title}>
  <Sidebar />
  <main class="page-main">
    <h1 class="page-title">Chemo-dynamical reconstruction</h1>

    <p>Chemo-dynamical reconstruction combines chemical abundances and kinematics to infer progenitor identities and assembly histories. Techniques include chemo-dynamical clustering and Bayesian reconstruction of age--metallicity relations.</p>

    <h2>Methods</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Hierarchical Bayesian CMD modelling</li>
      <li>Chemo-dynamical clustering using kinematics + abundances</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Key paper</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><WikiLink slug="pages/lardo_2026_gc_progenitors" text="Lardo et al. (2026)" /></li>
    </ul>
  </main>
</Base>
